transcript.text: Hi, we are happy to showcase our new 3D packaging solution.
Did you know the growing demand for packaging solutions has become undeniable?
Research says 61% of customers want to receive unique packaging and 68% of customers perceive a brand to be more upscale due to its packaging solution.

The 3D packaging solution is specially designed for print service providers to grow packaging and label print sales by offering easy online ordering, automating order management to make small orders profitable, increasing product portfolio, targeting niche segments, catering to different sales channels online designing and offering a world class post purchase experience to your clients.
Let's see how is the experience for your end clients in storefront.
Here is the product box where customer can enter length, width and depth.
Price will be calculated by our dynamic price calculator.
When you click on custom design, you will be in Designer Studio where you can customize box from inside as well as outside.
You can also update length, width and depth from Designer studio and canvas will change according to it.
Now let me show you the created design and how it looks like.
Here you can see the 3D preview of box.
3D preview will show real time changes.
You can see the real time changes as I am changing it.
Grow your personalized label and packaging sales today with On Print Shop.
For more details, please visit us at WWW dot on printshop.com.
Thank you for watching this video.
